    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Cleric Training, Level 8+</p><p>You have grown in your faith, attaining the rank of Priest and the powers that come with it.</p><ul><li><p>You gain the rank of Priest in your Religion and gain the corresponding Priest talents.</p></li><li><p>If you don't have enough Mana to cast a spell, you can spend your Inspiration to cast any spell from your religion at a Rank at which you are capable of casting.</p></li><li><p>You are limited to a maximum Spell Rank of 4 when casting as a Cleric.</p></li></ul>",
